2*. Run a container that outputs the current date and time in Rome. Should be only Dockerfile.(Tip: user 'tzdata' library)

liudmyla@liudmyla-MS-7636:~/cursor_git/HW9$ docker build . -t rome_time
Sending build context to Docker daemon  225.3MB
Step 1/2 : FROM ubuntu
 ---> 7e0aa2d69a15
Step 2/2 : CMD TZ=Italy/Rome date
 ---> Running in 2ee61b687bd2
Removing intermediate container 2ee61b687bd2
 ---> 6c03bfe35c0d
Successfully built 6c03bfe35c0d
Successfully tagged rome_time:latest
liudmyla@liudmyla-MS-7636:~/cursor_git/HW9$ docker run 6c03bfe35c0d
Tue Jun 15 14:36:24 Italy 2021
